stories.seoTitle: Sikandar Raza, Brendan Taylor tons power Zimbabwe to massive win
stories.summary: The pair added 173 for the fifth wicket to drive the hosts to a total of 380 for 6; Raza followed up with three wickets to help wrap up a 116-run win
